      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231364/Lens_image1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330712471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231364/Lens_image1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330712471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"360\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231380\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lens_image1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231364\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"55bc4bcb-a9ac-4276-a1e2-f82c110dda22\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231364/Lens_image1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330712471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231364/Lens_image1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330712471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span><p /><p><br/></p><p>PRMan has the ability to create custom RixProjection plugins. These plugins can be used to characterize camera and lens projections. The distribution includes several built-in plugins, as well. Note that whether or not the depth of field and bokeh settings apply to projection plugins depends on the individual plugin. Below we explain the most common and full-featured projection plugin.</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231407/PxrCamera\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrCamera</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231871/PxrPanini\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrPanini</a><br/><br/></p></li></ul>"
